reviews.review_text: stir it up who's on vocals???

That Was Bobby... ...who was trying to sing...clearly he could not remember much more than the chorus. So much for bustouts. I wouldn't dignify _Stir It Up_ with a proper title/slot in the set list any more than I would the _So What_ noodle-fest that they play on the third night while waiting for Bobby to come out onstage at the start of the 2nd set. This doesn't mean that they weren't fun shows; I had a BLAST.
